aces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果冇錯既7點無記應該唔會係播劇, 一係唔係81, 一係就6點/10點,<br />\n你上維基搵啦, 應該有link 睇番之前做咩</blockquote><br />\n謝ching回覆，我google過先黎架，佢wiki古裝加埋成千套，filter完，問誰領風騷個beat有d似但唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446c615ab2f07ffb21026823c200fea66fad4a58","tid":268701,"uid":93816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mi Mi Fa So So Fa Mi Re Do Do Re Mi Mi- ReRe<br />\nMi Mi Fa So So Fa Mi Re Do Do Re Mi Re- DoDo<br />\nRe Re Mi Do Re MiFa Mi Do Re MiFa Mi Re Do Re So<br />\nMi Mi Fa So So Fa Mi Re Do Do Re Mi Re- DoDo</blockquote><br />\n應該係呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91a6b44a545756d6612084f4788b361fb2bf24e","tid":268701,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係一套198x 年嘅古裝劇，幾年前喺tvb大約朝早7點重播，好可能係元朝劇，我淨係記得個intro嘅音樂係吹住隻號角： do do do do do<br />\n個tone 大約係me me fa so so<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果冇錯既7點無記應該唔會係播劇, 一係唔係81, 一係就6點/10點,<br />\n你上維基搵啦, 應該有link 睇番之前做咩</blockquote><br />\n謝ching回覆，我google過先黎架，佢wiki古裝加埋成千套，filter完，問誰領風騷個beat有d似但唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係咁search 呀, 我指例如係<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/翡翠台電視劇集列表_(2016年)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%BF%A1%E7%BF%A0%E5%8F%B0%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8A%87%E9%9B%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8_%282016%E5%B9%B4%29&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsQRJEaK469wi7